_sText:
This is my third map I have ever made for CS:S so please be gentle.
Instead of showing off what I have learned on hammer editor, I tried to make a map that was actually fun to play, and this is the result! I hope you like it, this is meant for GG
(note: I lovingly used another persons sun and sunlight, which was provided in their tutorial on how to make light with a sun_env entity, but I forgot their name)
